title: X-Plane 11 - Aircraft Megapack (Payware+Freeware)
description:
I've been playing X-Plane 11 for over a year now and checking pirating websites every week. I downloaded a bunch of interesting aircraft over those years and decided that people might like it if I share some of them. I didn't crack any of these myself and I'm only providing an easy way to expand your X-Plane aircraft library. Sorry if you feel like I'm stealing your credit, but the crackers are hardly ever listed in the actual aircraft folders so I couldn't really list them all here. To those people, you know who you are and thank you for your work.

Aircraft included:

737 by IXEG
737NG by Zibo (freeware)
787-9 by VMAX
A320 by JARDesign (FlightFactor hasn't been cracked yet unfortunately)
A330 by JARDesign
A380 by riviere (not a very realistic model, freeware)
Alphajet A
ATR 72-500 by Aerosoft
AeroBoero AB-115
Beechcraft A36 Bonanza by Carenado
Beechcraft F33A Bonanza by Carenado
Boeing 737 by FlyJSim
Boeing 757 by FlightFactor
Boeing 767 by FlightFactor
Boeing 777 by FlightFactor
Cessna C208B Grand Caravan by Carenado
Cessna 206H Stationair by Carenado
Cessna 340 by Carenado
DHC-6 Twin Otter by RWDesign
Douglas DC3/C47 by VSKYLABS
Embraer E195 by XCraft
Let L-410
Lockheed-Martin C130
McDonnel Douglas MD-80 (RotateSim)
Mooney M20 Juliet (Carenado)
Pilatus PC-12 (Carenado)

Thanks to the crackers and developers!
